122
00:07:17,583 --> 00:07:21,451
Yeah, Dwayne.
Get her inside.

123
00:07:21,453 --> 00:07:23,887
Tyler? Tyler?

124
00:07:32,897 --> 00:07:35,399
She's in
the back country,

125
00:07:35,401 --> 00:07:38,251
