145
00:08:37,629 --> 00:08:40,580
Bullies, huh?
Yeah.

146
00:08:40,582 --> 00:08:42,999
Wonder what'd happen if
you saw those guys now.

147
00:08:43,001 --> 00:08:45,034
I bet you'd tear
them apart, right?

148
00:08:45,036 --> 00:08:47,838
Ah, yeah, totally.

149
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:51,341
