to wait in the car.

161
00:09:22,925 --> 00:09:25,208
Do be certain to leave
the windows down.

162
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:27,427
Ah, so I've
touched a nerve.

163
00:09:27,429 --> 00:09:29,679
You've begun
to admire this girl.

164
00:09:29,681 --> 00:09:31,598
