183
00:10:16,678 --> 00:10:22,148
although I didn't give him
much choice in the matter.

184
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:24,935
He was loyal
in the beginning,

185
00:10:24,937 --> 00:10:26,653
but he grew
insubordinate,

186
00:10:26,655 --> 00:10:28,271
