is to flip Josh.

222
00:12:05,776 --> 00:12:08,277
That way, he can tell Klaus
whatever I want.

223
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:09,895
He could even
spy for me.

224
00:12:09,897 --> 00:12:12,114
