Dwayne comes in.

288
00:16:25,315 --> 00:16:27,315
You see, he was happy
to be the test case.

289
00:16:27,317 --> 00:16:28,482
If you haven't noticed,
these people

290
00:16:28,484 --> 00:16:29,868
